[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 1.58,
    "text": "You know why we're here today?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1.58,
    "endTime": 2.3200000000000003,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.6,
    "endTime": 5.28,
    "text": "Well, we're here to talk about Santa Claus."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.42,
    "endTime": 7.6,
    "text": "Where does Santa Claus live?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.6,
    "endTime": 10.0,
    "text": "I know! Um, the North Pole."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.44,
    "endTime": 12.02,
    "text": "What else do you know about Santa?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.8,
    "endTime": 12.959000000000001,
    "text": "He's chubby."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.02,
    "endTime": 15.42,
    "text": "- Too much cookies huh? -Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.56,
    "endTime": 17.7,
    "text": "Well, mom and I got something we need to tell you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.38,
    "endTime": 20.38,
    "text": "Can we break some news to them?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.52,
    "endTime": 21.93,
    "text": "- We're just telling him? - Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.93,
    "endTime": 24.27,
    "text": "Oh. (laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.78,
    "endTime": 25.98,
    "text": "Santa isn't real."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.24,
    "endTime": 33.62,
    "text": "Do I ever tell you Santa Claus is not real?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.36,
    "endTime": 37.04,
    "text": "No, I just figured that one out. (laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.56,
    "endTime": 39.719,
    "text": "This is Mrs. Claus and this is Santa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.2,
    "endTime": 41.42,
    "text": "I knew it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.8,
    "endTime": 42.559999999999995,
    "text": "I kinda knew it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.64,
    "endTime": 45.379,
    "text": "Santa Claus is not real."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.92,
    "endTime": 47.28,
    "text": "I told ya."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.88,
    "endTime": 48.440000000000005,
    "text": "I told you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.02,
    "endTime": 50.34,
    "text": "You know that Santa's not real?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.64,
    "endTime": 55.3,
    "text": "Err. Wrong."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.3,
    "endTime": 56.458999999999996,
    "text": "Santa Claus is real."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.36,
    "endTime": 58.9,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.66,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "Where at?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
    "endTime": 63.34,
    "text": "Cascade Mall and the line was huge."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.78,
    "endTime": 66.54,
    "text": "Well, Santa's not real, sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.84,
    "endTime": 71.72,
    "text": "Have you ever wondered how Santa can be at every mall in all these different places at one time?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.98,
    "endTime": 76.48,
    "text": "The more people that believe in Santa Claus, the more power he has to fly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.78,
    "endTime": 77.28,
    "text": "Ohh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.79,
    "endTime": 80.4,
    "text": "Mommy is the one that writes \"from Santa\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.4,
    "endTime": 81.81,
    "text": "So she's lying to you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.88,
    "endTime": 84.24,
    "text": "She's a liar."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.68,
    "endTime": 86.16000000000001,
    "text": "Mommy just reads it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.16,
    "endTime": 87.58,
    "text": "And then I throw it away."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.92,
    "endTime": 88.42,
    "text": "Mom!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.68,
    "endTime": 90.48,
    "text": "(laughing)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.4,
    "endTime": 93.14,
    "text": "But she's Mrs. Santa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.32,
    "endTime": 94.279,
    "text": "No you're not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.52,
    "endTime": 96.72,
    "text": "Mrs. Santa has white hair."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.18,
    "endTime": 98.14,
    "text": "But you have dark hair."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.04,
    "endTime": 99.80000000000001,
    "text": "But do you remember one time you asked me, you said,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.869,
    "endTime": 104.329,
    "text": "\"Why Santa Claus come down from chimney but he did not get a burn?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.44,
    "endTime": 112.28,
    "text": "Every single person that celebrates Christmas does not like put their chimney on fire."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.54,
    "endTime": 113.14,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.14,
    "endTime": 115.26,
    "text": "Nobody wants to kill Santa Claus. Nobody does."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.18,
    "endTime": 120.02000000000001,
    "text": "Well, mommy really feel like we're a terrible person now because we are telling the truth."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.0,
    "endTime": 121.96,
    "text": "Santa Claus is not real."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.13,
    "endTime": 123.449,
    "text": "You are not telling the truth."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.96,
    "endTime": 128.97899999999998,
    "text": "Yes, it actually depends what the situation is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.34,
    "endTime": 130.56,
    "text": "The situation is,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.74,
    "endTime": 133.14000000000001,
    "text": "telling you that Santa isn't real."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.14,
    "endTime": 134.94,
    "text": "I don't believe that situation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.34,
    "endTime": 138.559,
    "text": "But mom and I bring you gifts."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.58,
    "endTime": 144.26000000000002,
    "text": "What happens to little boys and girls that don't believe in Santa Claus?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.26,
    "endTime": 144.78,
    "text": "Well."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.78,
    "endTime": 146.46,
    "text": "They do Kwanzaa or Hannukah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.74,
    "endTime": 150.26000000000002,
    "text": "Well. Besides that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.16,
    "endTime": 152.24,
    "text": "You're getting older Kayla."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.52,
    "endTime": 155.4,
    "text": "So it's time for you to know that Santa's not even real."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.4,
    "endTime": 155.9,
    "text": "It is real."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.89,
    "endTime": 158.29,
    "text": "What's your idea though?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.54,
    "endTime": 160.35899999999998,
    "text": "My idea is that's a big fake."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.4,
    "endTime": 162.44,
    "text": "And no. Santa is real."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.5,
    "endTime": 165.64,
    "text": "Well, I think we all have a little..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.64,
    "endTime": 166.23899999999998,
    "text": "Case closed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.68,
    "endTime": 170.46,
    "text": "And you remember when you put milk and cookies?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.7,
    "endTime": 173.6,
    "text": "I was the one who drank the milk."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.76,
    "endTime": 175.2,
    "text": "So you were Santa?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.42,
    "endTime": 176.78,
    "text": "I was the fake Santa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.64,
    "endTime": 183.0,
    "text": "So then all this time, I've been thinking that Santa ate the cookies?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.16,
    "endTime": 185.14,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.1,
    "endTime": 186.92,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.36,
    "endTime": 189.82000000000002,
    "text": "But the cookies are really good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.96,
    "endTime": 193.06,
    "text": "Why don't you want to believe the situation?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.12,
    "endTime": 196.459,
    "text": "Cuz Santa is real."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.1,
    "endTime": 198.06,
    "text": "No he's not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.18,
    "endTime": 198.68,
    "text": "Yes he is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.68,
    "endTime": 199.18,
    "text": "Nope!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.32,
    "endTime": 199.82,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.82,
    "endTime": 200.38,
    "text": "Sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.5,
    "endTime": 201.0,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.14,
    "endTime": 202.22,
    "text": "Sorry! You're out of luck."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.54,
    "endTime": 203.2,
    "text": "What do you think?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.4,
    "endTime": 204.38,
    "text": "Whatever."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.54,
    "endTime": 205.04,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.52,
    "endTime": 208.96,
    "text": "Don't look at me mean!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.72,
    "endTime": 214.52,
    "text": "The Michael Jackson song we listened to all the time \"I Saw Mommy Kissing Santa Claus,\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.62,
    "endTime": 216.75,
    "text": "you wanna know why mommy was kissing Santa Claus?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.75,
    "endTime": 217.44,
    "text": "And Daddy wasn't there?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.44,
    "endTime": 219.26,
    "text": "Daddy did not hear. Daddy did not see it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.26,
    "endTime": 220.35899999999998,
    "text": "What is going on?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.36,
    "endTime": 222.16000000000003,
    "text": "Because Daddy IS Santa Claus."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.17,
    "endTime": 224.13,
    "text": "And that's the reason Mommy kissed Santa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.62,
    "endTime": 226.74,
    "text": "Your life is a lie. Tria."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.9,
    "endTime": 228.44,
    "text": "I'm just kidding, you're fine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.62,
    "endTime": 229.3,
    "text": "Ok look."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.3,
    "endTime": 233.20000000000002,
    "text": "I could prove that you two, you're not Santa and you're not Ms. Claus."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.22,
    "endTime": 234.1,
    "text": "Ok, prove it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.36,
    "endTime": 237.10000000000002,
    "text": "Ask me a question that only Santa would know the answer to."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.02,
    "endTime": 239.28,
    "text": "Tell me all the reindeer names."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.7,
    "endTime": 243.92,
    "text": "Well, there's Dancer and Prancer and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.92,
    "endTime": 245.1,
    "text": "Qbert."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.1,
    "endTime": 245.94,
    "text": "(Maddox laughing)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.8,
    "endTime": 247.3,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.3,
    "endTime": 248.22,
    "text": "You're not Santa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.4,
    "endTime": 248.92000000000002,
    "text": "How many did I say?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.8,
    "endTime": 251.10000000000002,
    "text": "You feel okay with that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.1,
    "endTime": 251.6,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.56,
    "endTime": 252.98,
    "text": "I see some tears."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.28,
    "endTime": 253.92,
    "text": "You okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.08,
    "endTime": 254.58,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.0,
    "endTime": 255.94,
    "text": "Are you going to still cooking?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.1,
    "endTime": 256.6,
    "text": "Mmhmm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.8,
    "endTime": 258.06,
    "text": "Your cookies are really good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.56,
    "endTime": 260.68,
    "text": "(both laughing)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.64,
    "endTime": 264.24,
    "text": "I make them with all my heart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.44,
    "endTime": 264.94,
    "text": "Awww"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.29,
    "endTime": 268.02000000000004,
    "text": "I think if Santa's real in your heart, then he should be real."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.08,
    "endTime": 270.2,
    "text": "And you should look forward to him on Christmas Day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 270.72,
    "endTime": 272.0,
    "text": "You have everything you want?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.36,
    "endTime": 272.98,
    "text": "Sort of, yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.26,
    "endTime": 274.12,
    "text": "You have me and your mom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.56,
    "endTime": 275.12,
    "text": "I know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.12,
    "endTime": 276.12,
    "text": "That's all you need right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.48,
    "endTime": 277.12,
    "text": "(shrugs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.28,
    "endTime": 277.78,
    "text": "(Dad laughing)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.42,
    "endTime": 280.46000000000004,
    "text": "What's Christmas all about you guys?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.76,
    "endTime": 281.36,
    "text": "Family."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.52,
    "endTime": 282.159,
    "text": "Family?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.7,
    "endTime": 284.2,
    "text": "I want you to be Santa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.2,
    "endTime": 285.599,
    "text": "You want me to be Santa?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.6,
    "endTime": 286.1,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.1,
    "endTime": 287.03000000000003,
    "text": "I'll be Santa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287.22,
    "endTime": 288.5,
    "text": "I'm the Santa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.5,
    "endTime": 289.46,
    "text": "No you're not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 290.54,
    "endTime": 292.06,
    "text": "You don't believe me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292.24,
    "endTime": 292.88,
    "text": "(laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.46,
    "endTime": 296.099,
    "text": "Why do you not believe me that I'm Santa?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.26,
    "endTime": 298.8,
    "text": "I think that you're my wish person."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 299.0,
    "endTime": 301.06,
    "text": "I'm the wish person?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301.06,
    "endTime": 302.4,
    "text": "What's a wish person?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302.96,
    "endTime": 305.34,
    "text": "Sometimes you make my wishes come true."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306.58,
    "endTime": 307.919,
    "text": "While we're here being truthful,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 307.92,
    "endTime": 309.28000000000003,
    "text": "do you know who the Tooth Fairy is?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309.28,
    "endTime": 309.84,
    "text": "Oh yay!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 311.02,
    "endTime": 311.52,
    "text": "It's your mother."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 311.82,
    "endTime": 312.36,
    "text": "Nope!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 314.0,
    "endTime": 318.1,
    "text": "So you met Santa Claus at your school the other day, at the pancake breakfast at your school."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 318.74,
    "endTime": 320.86,
    "text": "Yeah, but that's the fake Santa Claus."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 320.86,
    "endTime": 322.90000000000003,
    "text": "That's Santa Claus's helper though."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 323.07,
    "endTime": 324.909,
    "text": "How do you know it was a fake Santa?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 325.06,
    "endTime": 327.36,
    "text": "Oh snap! That's a good question."
  }
]